120 Giornate Di Sodoma (DvdRip / Classic / 1995)

Before The French revolution came along and spoiled their fun, the rich aristocrats spent most of their time indulging in the pleasures of the flesh- on a grand scale. Huge Banquets would be laid out for the so-called &quot;ladies and gentlemen&quot; of the court- with the main course being an orgy of unbridled debauchery. Shot entirely on film by Europe's acclaimed director Joe D'Amato, ANAL PALACE, is a lavish period production that lives up to its portrayal of the &quot;beautiful people&quot; and their pursuit of pleasure in every possible form. Shot on location in Europe with an all-star cast from America and abroad, this beautiful, sensual, and provocative film celebrates the art of making love- with a decidedly kinky twist.

Anita Blond, Kelly Trump, Deborah Wells, Shalimar (as Cheyenne), Bernadette Manfredi, Backey Jakic, Frank Gun (as Frank Mallone), Mark Davis, Sean Michaels

